aily.com/local/daily/article/20190813/20748071</a><br />\n<br />\n811 飛虎扮示威者挑打鬥再拉人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190812/20747590\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F20747590&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAAWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=e6735a05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F20747590&h=9f3513fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190812/20747590</a><br />\n<br />\n811 多區民居中招 警射入葵芳站 催淚彈恐襲<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190812/20747634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F20747634&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAAWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=1a0f11d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F20747634&h=dc73eea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190812/20747634</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qp69gNr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqp69gNr.png&h=869a257d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">政府而家同黑社會同黑警同我地香港人玩shot to kill 呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全世界即刻同我去做文宣，推行動post，咪撚再打飛機！</span></span>"},{"pid":"592843c3deb168b66d1f39f2fddf61f21acb239a","tid":1488801,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:57:36.000Z","msg":"香港人唔好忘記 我地有6個手足死左 700個人被捕 一個盲左 無數個受傷呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">我地開心既時候佢地日日都擔心緊呀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7月1號明明講好左無論發生咩事都一齊<img src=\"/assets/face